<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="deserve-vt">deserve <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'zɜːv/    美 /dɪ'zɜːrv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于进行时] 应受；值得</strong></h4>
<p>to earn sth, either good or bad, because of sth that you have done：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>deserve a rest</strong> after all that hard work. 
劳累了这么久，你应该好好休息一下。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What comes first is to keep an open mind, because everyone’s ideas <strong>deserve consideration</strong>.  
首先要保持一个开放的心态，因为每个人的想法都值得考虑。</p><footer>2008 江苏改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>deserve to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She deserves to succeed. 
她应该成功。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s true that she made a mistake but she hardly deserves to lose her job. 
她的确犯了错，但她不应该被解雇。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>deserve doing / deserve to be done：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s a responsible writer, and he deserves respecting / to be respected. 
他是个有责任感的作家，理应受人尊敬。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>deserved /dɪ'zɜːvd/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>well-deserved rest</strong>
应得的休息</p></div>

<p>deserving /dɪ'zɜːvɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an issue <strong>deserving of</strong> attention
值得注意的问题</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the deserving poor 
值得帮助的穷人</p></div></div>